"{\"uid\": \"greekreporter.com-2024-08-15-ai-heating-olympic-pool\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"The growing use ofartificial intelligence (AI)is creating a greater demand for data centers.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 92, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The growing use ofartificial intelligence\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 41}, {\"ngram\": \"a greater demand\", \"from\": 58, \"to\": 74}, {\"ngram\": \"data centers\", \"from\": 79, \"to\": 91}]}, {\"sentence\": \"These AI data centers generate a lot of heat, but one of these is putting that heat to good use for the Paris Summer Olympics swimming pool.\", \"from\": 93, \"to\": 233, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 99, \"end\": 101, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"score\": 0.9999995241279289, \"rank\": 4.757856907735906e-07, \"text\": \"AI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 124, \"to\": 129}, {\"ngram\": \"heat\", \"from\": 133, \"to\": 137}, {\"ngram\": \"that heat\", \"from\": 167, \"to\": 176}, {\"ngram\": \"good use\", \"from\": 180, \"to\": 188}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Summer Olympics swimming pool\", \"from\": 193, \"to\": 232}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A US company, Equinix, owns a data center that produces extra heat from its many servers.\", \"from\": 235, \"to\": 324, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 237, \"end\": 239, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_dollar\", \"score\": 0.6388168487544265, \"rank\": 0.5653189294064301, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_dollar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_dollar\"}, {\"begin\": 249, \"end\": 256, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equinix\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Equinix\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equinix\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equinix\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a data center\", \"from\": 263, \"to\": 276}, {\"ngram\": \"extra heat\", \"from\": 291, \"to\": 301}, {\"ngram\": \"its many servers\", \"from\": 307, \"to\": 323}]}, {\"sentence\": \"According to FOX Business, instead of allowing the heat to be wasted, the company is channeling it to warm the swimming pool at the nearby Paris Olympics Aquatics Centre, ensuring it's comfortably warm for athletes.\", \"from\": 325, \"to\": 540, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 338, \"end\": 350, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_Business\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"FOX Business\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_Business\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_Business\"}, {\"begin\": 464, \"end\": 478, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the heat\", \"from\": 372, \"to\": 380}, {\"ngram\": \"the company\", \"from\": 395, \"to\": 406}, {\"ngram\": \"the swimming pool\", \"from\": 432, \"to\": 449}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 531, \"to\": 539}]}, {\"sentence\": \"AI data centers use immense amounts of energy to run large groups of servers.\", \"from\": 542, \"to\": 619, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 542, \"end\": 544, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"score\": 0.9999995241279289, \"rank\": 4.757856907735906e-07, \"text\": \"AI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"immense amounts\", \"from\": 562, \"to\": 577}, {\"ngram\": \"energy\", \"from\": 581, \"to\": 587}, {\"ngram\": \"large groups\", \"from\": 595, \"to\": 607}, {\"ngram\": \"servers\", \"from\": 611, \"to\": 618}]}, {\"sentence\": \"These servers work with data to train AI programs, such as ChatGPT.\", \"from\": 620, \"to\": 687, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 658, \"end\": 660, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"score\": 0.9999995241279289, \"rank\": 4.757856907735906e-07, \"text\": \"AI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"These servers\", \"from\": 620, \"to\": 633}, {\"ngram\": \"data\", \"from\": 644, \"to\": 648}, {\"ngram\": \"ChatGPT\", \"from\": 679, \"to\": 686}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Keeping these servers cool is important because they can get quite hot, often even getting hotter than 80 degrees Fahrenheit.\", \"from\": 688, \"to\": 813, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 802, \"end\": 812, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fahrenheit\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.2565432136769527e-31, \"text\": \"Fahrenheit\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fahrenheit\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fahrenheit\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"these servers\", \"from\": 696, \"to\": 709}, {\"ngram\": \"80 degrees\", \"from\": 791, \"to\": 801}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To cool them down, fans and liquid cooling systems are commonly used.\", \"from\": 814, \"to\": 883, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"fans\", \"from\": 833, \"to\": 837}, {\"ngram\": \"liquid cooling systems\", \"from\": 842, \"to\": 864}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One such data center, known as PA10, was opened by Equinix in 2023 at their campus in Saint-Denis, France.\", \"from\": 885, \"to\": 991, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 936, \"end\": 943, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equinix\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Equinix\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equinix\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equinix\"}, {\"begin\": 971, \"end\": 982, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"score\": 0.6536924012812751, \"rank\": 0.5219366732171404, \"text\": \"Saint-Denis\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\"}, {\"begin\": 984, \"end\": 990, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9998271949720833, \"rank\": 0.00010514071334617919, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"One such data center\", \"from\": 885, \"to\": 905}, {\"ngram\": \"PA10\", \"from\": 916, \"to\": 920}, {\"ngram\": \"their campus\", \"from\": 955, \"to\": 967}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This center is built to handle powerful server setups that trainAI models.\", \"from\": 992, \"to\": 1066, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This center\", \"from\": 992, \"to\": 1003}, {\"ngram\": \"powerful server setups\", \"from\": 1023, \"to\": 1045}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It also uses special technology to export excess heat generated by the servers.\", \"from\": 1067, \"to\": 1146, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"special technology\", \"from\": 1080, \"to\": 1098}, {\"ngram\": \"excess heat\", \"from\": 1109, \"to\": 1120}, {\"ngram\": \"the servers\", \"from\": 1134, \"to\": 1145}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Equinix informed Wired that they anticipate exporting 6.6 thermal megawatts of heat from their data center when it's fully operational.\", \"from\": 1148, \"to\": 1283, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1148, \"end\": 1155, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equinix\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Equinix\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equinix\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equinix\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Wired\", \"from\": 1165, \"to\": 1170}, {\"ngram\": \"6.6 thermal megawatts\", \"from\": 1202, \"to\": 1223}, {\"ngram\": \"heat\", \"from\": 1227, \"to\": 1231}, {\"ngram\": \"their data center\", \"from\": 1237, \"to\": 1254}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This amount of heat could help keep more than a thousand homes warm.\", \"from\": 1284, \"to\": 1352, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This amount\", \"from\": 1284, \"to\": 1295}, {\"ngram\": \"heat\", \"from\": 1299, \"to\": 1303}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A data center owned by@Equinixis capturing and reusing heat produced by servers to funnel heat that helps keep the swimming pool at Paris@OlympicsAquatics Centre.\", \"from\": 1354, \"to\": 1516, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A data center\", \"from\": 1354, \"to\": 1367}, {\"ngram\": \"heat\", \"from\": 1409, \"to\": 1413}, {\"ngram\": \"servers\", \"from\": 1426, \"to\": 1433}, {\"ngram\": \"heat\", \"from\": 1444, \"to\": 1448}, {\"ngram\": \"the swimming pool\", \"from\": 1465, \"to\": 1482}, {\"ngram\": \"Paris@OlympicsAquatics Centre\", \"from\": 1486, \"to\": 1515}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As an energy source it will spare the region 1,800 metric tons of CO2 emissions per year.\", \"from\": 1517, \"to\": 1606, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an energy source\", \"from\": 1520, \"to\": 1536}, {\"ngram\": \"the region\", \"from\": 1551, \"to\": 1561}, {\"ngram\": \"1,800 metric tons\", \"from\": 1562, \"to\": 1579}, {\"ngram\": \"CO2 emissions\", \"from\": 1583, \"to\": 1596}, {\"ngram\": \"year\", \"from\": 1601, \"to\": 1605}]}, {\"sentence\": \"@Paris2024pic.twitter.com/CbfgTOLLji - Pick Up Project \\ud83c\\udf0e (@Pick_Up_Project)August 10, 2024 To help heat the pool at theOlympic Aquatics Centre, Equinix partnered with a French utility company, Engie.\", \"from\": 1606, \"to\": 1809, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1755, \"end\": 1762, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equinix\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Equinix\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equinix\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equinix\"}, {\"begin\": 1780, \"end\": 1786, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.7268358528458341, \"rank\": 0.3397567518387263, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 1804, \"end\": 1809, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Engie\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Engie\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Engie\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Engie\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Project \\ud83c\\udf0e\", \"from\": 1653, \"to\": 1662}, {\"ngram\": \"@Pick_Up_Project)August\", \"from\": 1664, \"to\": 1687}, {\"ngram\": \"the pool\", \"from\": 1710, \"to\": 1718}, {\"ngram\": \"theOlympic Aquatics Centre\", \"from\": 1722, \"to\": 1748}, {\"ngram\": \"Engie\", \"from\": 1799, \"to\": 1804}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They redirected the excess heat from the data center into Engie's energy system through pipes.\", \"from\": 1810, \"to\": 1904, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1869, \"end\": 1874, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Engie\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Engie\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Engie\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Engie\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the excess heat\", \"from\": 1826, \"to\": 1841}, {\"ngram\": \"the data center\", \"from\": 1847, \"to\": 1862}, {\"ngram\": \"pipes\", \"from\": 1898, \"to\": 1903}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The heat is then used to warm the aquatics center's pool, as well as heat about 600 nearby homes and local businesses, according to FOX Business.\", \"from\": 1906, \"to\": 2051, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2039, \"end\": 2051, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_Business\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"FOX Business\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_Business\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_Business\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The heat\", \"from\": 1906, \"to\": 1914}, {\"ngram\": \"the aquatics center's pool\", \"from\": 1936, \"to\": 1962}, {\"ngram\": \"about 600 nearby homes\", \"from\": 1980, \"to\": 2002}, {\"ngram\": \"local businesses\", \"from\": 2007, \"to\": 2023}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The new setup benefits Equinix, as well, allowing the company to utilize less energy for its cooling system by exporting excess heat.\", \"from\": 2053, \"to\": 2186, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2077, \"end\": 2084, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equinix\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Equinix\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equinix\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equinix\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The new setup\", \"from\": 2053, \"to\": 2066}, {\"ngram\": \"the company\", \"from\": 2103, \"to\": 2114}, {\"ngram\": \"less energy\", \"from\": 2126, \"to\": 2137}, {\"ngram\": \"its cooling system\", \"from\": 2142, \"to\": 2160}, {\"ngram\": \"excess heat\", \"from\": 2174, \"to\": 2185}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Additionally, Equinix has established a rooftop greenhouse on top of the data center.\", \"from\": 2187, \"to\": 2272, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2202, \"end\": 2209, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equinix\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Equinix\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equinix\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equinix\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a rooftop greenhouse\", \"from\": 2225, \"to\": 2245}, {\"ngram\": \"top\", \"from\": 2249, \"to\": 2252}, {\"ngram\": \"the data center\", \"from\": 2256, \"to\": 2271}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In this greenhouse, strawberries, tomatoes, and other plants are grown, using the heat that's redirected from the facility.\", \"from\": 2273, \"to\": 2396, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this greenhouse\", \"from\": 2276, \"to\": 2291}, {\"ngram\": \"strawberries\", \"from\": 2293, \"to\": 2305}, {\"ngram\": \"tomatoes\", \"from\": 2307, \"to\": 2315}, {\"ngram\": \"other plants\", \"from\": 2321, \"to\": 2333}, {\"ngram\": \"the heat\", \"from\": 2351, \"to\": 2359}, {\"ngram\": \"the facility\", \"from\": 2383, \"to\": 2395}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Noah Nkonge, who leads the heat export efforts at Equinix, shared on thecompany's websitethat the PA10 data center in Paris will provide surplus heat at no cost for 15 years.\", \"from\": 2398, \"to\": 2572, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2399, \"end\": 2403, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah\", \"score\": 0.9188706791060466, \"rank\": 0.0550302829732952, \"text\": \"Noah\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah\"}, {\"begin\": 2449, \"end\": 2456, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equinix\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Equinix\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equinix\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equinix\"}, {\"begin\": 2517, \"end\": 2522, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999719884731, \"rank\": 2.8011430954001843e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://db